  "text": "Amplicons of E. faecalis were generated using primer M13R2: GGAAACAGCTATGACCATGA [CITATION_1] . PCRconditions were denaturation at 95 • C for 15:00 (min:sec), followed by 40 cycles of melting at 94 • C for 00:30, annealing at 38 • C, 01:00, elongation at 72 • C, 01:00 and a final extension step at 72 • C for 05:00.",
